videos.description: Stefanie Dolson delivers a beautiful bounce pass to a cutting Allie Quigley, who finishes at the rim in traffic to score for the Sky.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Dolson feeds Quigley for backdoor bucket) 2020/9/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dolson feeds Quigley for backdoor bucket

videos.description: Alyssa Thomas gets an and-1 bucket in the post as part of her 26-point night in the Sun's 94-81 win over the Sky in the first round of the playoffs.
